==Trivia==
*On release, players could also get rewarded Botanical pies from master clues, but this drop was quickly removed after this reward crashed the market of botanical pies.
*With the [[Update:Barbarian Assault Ranged Rework|25 Jan 2018 update]] 3 new unique rewards were added to master clue scrolls, being the [[Anguish ornament kit]], [[Dragon platebody ornament kit]] and [[Dragon kiteshield ornament kit]].
*In 2016 Mod Mat K revealed in a [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m-5hXaHEzIM&t=465s data stream] that on average 700 master clue scrolls were completed every day.

